{"tid":2323993,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不少市民到大棠賞紅葉　部分疑違反限聚令","createTime":"2020-12-13T15:06:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T23:04:25.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"c69cced885d074da78516ec2ccc785c343d2f68a","tid":2323993,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T15:06:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565065-20201213.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565065-20201213.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mTcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=a8462a5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565065-20201213.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e1635b9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565065-20201213.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n本港疫情持續，有不少市民趁星期日到元朗大棠郊遊，欣賞紅葉。<br />\n<br />\n大棠的主要郊遊路徑人頭湧湧，記者現場所見，人與人之間未能經常保持1.5米社交距離。不少人都是一家幾口或多名朋友結伴同遊，懷疑超出「限聚令」2人的限制。市民都有戴口罩，不過亦有人除下口罩拍照。<br />\n<br />\n有市民說，現場人數眾多，有少許擔心感染風險；但亦有人表示不擔心，因為全程都有戴口罩。漁護署派人到場，並舉起提示牌，呼籲市民保持社交距離。"},{"pid":"a69611add2d6bbb0fae333aaa40b53ca0dce20fd","tid":2323993,"uid":22329,"like":63,"dislike":3,"score":60,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T15:09:15.000Z","msg":"搞到咁都係政府自己攞黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開頭d人都驚唔多點出街<br />\n<br />\n佢就一直放清兵入關<br />\n<br />\n好啦大家都無晒耐性<br />\n<br />\n咁咪仲好真攬炒"},{"pid":"0b13bcb894758b2ede1a446a416b76585d0b6fad","tid":2323993,"uid":220942,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T15:09:51.000Z","msg":"留名睇封山<br />\n食花生"},{"pid":"fe5db5561d1c06edaebb001d114d83f3d29189d2","tid":2323993,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T15:11:03.000Z","msg":"一般去到幾月完？"},{"pid":"f3d8cc21b28eed45c6e8b4b28b4471d4a3eb753b","tid":2323993,"uid":67500,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":